Increase in the volume of goods moving across borders between EAC countries and the rest of the continent;

Reduction in the number of NTB-related challenges to move across EAC borders

Enhanced capacity of EAC and member states to resolve NTBs and other Trade Disputes impacting the movement of goods across borders

